name: Rinatto L'bank Portrait 2016
description: I remember that day I was visiting my friends in the villa after a very difficult incident in my life. I didn't know if I would be free. I didn't know if my life would break down in a year or if it would make sense to start doing anything. But I decided that no matter what, I would start a project - and either it would be my new beginning or it would be for nothing. Since then I have continued to work on myself and my L'bank project  Translated with www.DeepL.com/Translator (free version)
